\c 25
\s Inkulumo yesithathu kaBilidadi: Uthi kakho umuntu ohlambulukileyo kuNkulunkulu
\p
\v 1 Wasephendula uBilidadi umShuhi wathi\x + 2.11.\x*:
\p
\v 2 Ukubusa lokwesabeka kulaye; uyenza ukuthula endaweni zakhe eziphezulu\x + 31.2. Isa. 24.21.\x*.
\v 3 Kukhona inani yini\x + Isa. 40.26.\x* lamabutho akhe\x + 19.12.\x*? Ngubani okungamphumeliyo ukukhanya kwakhe\x + Mat. 5.45. Jak. 1.17.\x*?
\v 4 Pho umuntu angalunga njani kuNkulunkulu\x + 4.17-19. 9.2. 15.14-16.\x*? Kumbe ozelwe ngowesifazana\x + 14.1.\x* angahlambuluka njani\x + 14.4.\x*?
\v 5 Khangela kuze kube senyangeni, njalo kayikhazimuli, lezinkanyezi kazihlambulukanga emehlweni akhe.
\v 6 Pho kangakanani umuntu \add oy\add*impethu\x + 9.14.15.16.\x*, lendodana yomuntu\x + 35.8.\x* \add eng\add*umswenya\x + Hlab. 22.6.\x*!